work.work-title: Heavenly Father, Thou hast brought us

encoding.software: PDFtoMusic Pro v1.6.5 Build 1B9E7 (c) Myriad - http://www.myriad-online.com

credit.credit-words: Mercies new and never-failing Brightly shine through all the past, Watchful care and loving-kindness Always near from first to last, Tender love, divine protection Ever with us day and night; Blessings more than we can number Strow the path with golden light.
Heavenly Father, Thou hast brought us

Many that we loved have left us, Reaching first their journey's end; Now they wait to give us welcome, Brother, sister, child, and friend. When at last our journey's over, And we pass away from sight, Father, take us through the darkness Into everlasting light.
